The paper deals with channel estimation for two-way relay networks, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of constant-modulus signaling is a common technique in signal processing (cs.SI) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the performance of different algorithms, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
